and I think Nick , he is risen very quickly , as people like Federer and Murray have pointed out , he is growing up in the public eye and he is made some terrible errors and deserves all the criticism he gets , but we are trying to support him , we are trying to help him understand the consequences of his actions , and some time out of the limelight where he can just reflect on that I think is appropriate and it is best for the team and it is best for him .
